Hati minggu kmrn niatnya buat buka puasa sama kluarga, siang hari reservasi ternyata disuruh Dateng sebelum jam 5. Kami Dateng jam 17.10 masih banyak tempat kosong, banyak yg baru datang juga. Dapet free takjil dan teh manis waktu menunggu sekitar setengah jam Krn terpotong kru nya buka puasa.
Ada yg beda dengan terakhir kami Dateng 7 THN yll, masih enak yg dulu. Harga agak mahal ya utk menu jamur. Jangan kuatir keabisan kursi Krn sekarang makin lebar

title: Jejamuran
name: desy widya
text: Terapi ikan gratis sambil nunggu makanan, penyajian cepeet, gaperlu bingung cari tempat duduk krn akn lsng diarahkan dr sana, kirain cuma makanan aja yg semuanya ttg jamur tnyta minuman jamur pun ada 😄 Harga msh terjangkau lah, parkir gratisss, pelayanan 👌

title: Jejamuran
name: Yoce Culandari Jovanka
text: Murah meriah lezaaat puaaas bgt makan disini makan sekeluarga bayar ky untuk 2 orang, hanya utk tempat baru kurang nyaman karna ataonya asbes panas dan klo ujan berisik

title: Jejamuran
name: Bima Ksatria
text:
Rasa masakannya enak nih... Walaupun isinya cuma jamur, tapi masaknya cukup serius.
Menu favorit so far: sate jamur, tongseng jamur dan sop jamur.
Penataan ruangan yg sekarang dibuat jd satu ruangan resto dgn banyak sekali meja.
Di pojok ada pemain karawitan.
Di pojok lain ada fish spa.. gratis.
Pojok satunya ada kolam ikan. Kao mau kasi makan beli aja di mini marketnya Rp 5rb.
Dapurnya gede bgt.
Penyajian makanan sangat cepat utk ukuran dan pengunjung yg sangat rame. Ngga sempet sebel pokoknya.
Parkiran luas bgt. Biasa menampung bus wisata.
Pertama masuk ke sini, pastikan ke lobby duluminta nomor meja. Stlh dpt nomor, silakan ke meja tsb di ruangan utama. Lalu pesan menu.
Pelayanan nya sgt ramah.

title: Jejamuran
name: Sutan Gibran
text:
Pilihan menunya lengkap.
Lokasi strategis dan mudah di cari.
Cocok untuk makan sekeluarga atau kelompok.

title: Jejamuran
name: Nur Muhammad Sholikhun
text: Menunya all jamur, banyak varian jamur juga yang bisa dinikmati. Rasa dari masakannya juga enak walau coba banyak menu tapi gak bikin enek walau semua dari jamur.

title: Jejamuran
name: ridwan surya
text:
Mantap nihh,pokoknya semua fnb enak bgt. Bersih tmptnya,luas,cocok bgt buat maen ama klrg n ponakan.
Hati2 ya klo dikasih meja ama mba receptionist di depan,minta agak tengah ato blkg aja,soalnya klo paling depan berisik bgt sama live musicnya.

title: Jejamuran
name: renaldy gunawan
text: Makanannya enak dan unik juga tidak mahal, tempatnya luas dan tersedia parkir.... pernah tidak kedapatan tempat karena sangat penuh.... pelayanannya cukup cepat

title: Jejamuran
name: Dini Andriani
text: Suasanya pas untuk makan besar bersama keluarga.. Konsep family restonya dapet.. Parkir luas nyaman.. Petugas nya ramah dan sangat membantu..  Kalo datang pas jam sibuk..  Kemungkinan akan waiting list.. Menunya banyak pilihan paket keluarga dengan harga affordable.. Rasa makanan sewajarnya..  Tapi konsep ruang nya bikin nyaman..

title: Jejamuran
name: james
text: tempatnya semakin nyaman, area parkir pun makin luas. makanannya semakin banyak pilihan dan enak. cocok untuk orang-orang vegetarian

title: Jejamuran
name: Gandhi Endrayanto
text: Jejamuran resto cocok bagi anda yang vegetarian,menyajikan berbagai olahan masakan serba jamur yang cukup enak sate jamurnya sekilas mirip sekali dengan sate daging/kambing,terdapat juga mini market yang menjual oleh oleh khas rumah makan jejamuran,tempat parkir cukup luas dan bersih,bagi yang penasaran & belum pernah kesini silahkan dicoba Jejamuran resto beralamat di Jalan Pendowoharjo Niron RT 01 RW 20, Niron, Pandowoharjo, Sleman Yogyakarta jam buka mulai pukul 09.00 s/d 21.10 WIB.

title: Jejamuran
name: Wahyu Permana
text: Lokasinya mudah ditemukan. Ada parkiran luas di seberangnya. Tempat makannya luas dan bersih. Ada toilet dan mushola juga. Sebelum masuk ada bilik disinfektan. Menu makanan utamanya olahan jamur. Dari penyajian di sate, rendang, krispi, gulai dan lain lain. Harganya cukup terjangkau. Bagi yang suka jamur, di sini surganya.

title: Jejamuran
name: anes aprilia
text: Harga termasuk murah...walau sy dtg saat long weekend penuh dan harus msk daftar waiting list tp cpet dpt kursinya....mknannya cepat datang...rasa oke...pelayanannya ramah....slama menunggu disambut icip2 tester kripik2 jamur dan brownies2 serta fish therapy dr para ikan gragas...😁😁...yg kurang ac aja gerah...

title: Jejamuran
name: ambrosius hestu
text: Tempatnya nyaman, masakan enak meskipun harganya cukup Mahal utk olahan jamur

title: Jejamuran
name: RICH HEUU
text: Resto yg unik,dimana semua menu dari bahan jamur, pelayanan ramah, parkiran luas,dan terdapat atm center

title: Jejamuran
name: Nur Hasanah
text: Tempatnya bagus, nyaman… cuma kalau laper dan lagi ngirit jangan kesini deh 😂, kasian kantongnya. Untuk sate jamur dibandrol harga 20rbuan lebih, diatas 15k semua ya, belum nasi

title: Jejamuran
name: KEISYU Chanel
text: Istimewa Utk sate am tongseng jamur y.harga standard... cm masakan msh blm komplit,ga tau ap karena trlalu pagi saya dsteng y😄

title: Jejamuran
name: GLEYAR GLEYOR
text: Cocok untuk yang vegetarian karena banyak menu berbahan dasar jamur

title: Jejamuran
name: BB BB
text: parkiran nya luas. berada di seberang jalan. sebelum masuk ke tempat makan nya disambut jamur - jamur berbagai macam. niatnya bagus, sayangnya tidak disertai nama dan keterangan / penjelasannya. saat masuk disambut oleh petugas di depan, langsung dipilihkan nomor tempat duduk, jadi tidak bisa memilih sendiri. jika kurang beruntung dapat tempat duduk yang tidak ada pemandangannya. tempat terbuka nya ada di area jalan keluar. makanannya enak, harga nya sesuai seperti resto - resto pada kelasnya. datangnya makanan pun juga cepat walaupun keadaan resto sedang ramai

title: Jejamuran
name: fitriana mide
text: Semua menu utama terbuat dari Jamur .. semua enak, tapi ada beberapa yang cenderung manis, namanya juga masakan Jawa .. saya tidak tahu apakah ada sambal atau tidak, tapi untuk pecinta pedas mungkin harus minta sambal .. bisa pesan menu lain bagi yang tidak suka jamur .. tapi buat apa ke sini kalau mau makan yang lain ?? Bisa lihat semua jenis jamur yang mereka masak di sini,, karena mereka memajang sebagian jamur yang mereka budidayakan sendiri ..

title: Jejamuran
name: Amin Fauzi
text: Dulu sempet nyobain beberapa menu disini dan rasanya memang enak sih,

title: Jejamuran
name: dont subscribe
text:
Lg pandemi jd lengang bgt biasanya wuih rameee..
Makannya selalu enak hanya saja sop jamurnya tdk terlalu panas

title: Jejamuran
name: Muhamad Sean
text: Tempat makan yang sangat menarik karena menyajikan makanan yang serba jamur. Datang kesini ketika jam makan siang dan weekdays tapi tempatnya tetap ramai. Untuk makanan yaaa lumayan lah, highlightnya mungkin sate jamurnya kali ya karna rasanya enak hampir mirip dengan daging ayam.

title: Jejamuran
name: Titis Ambarwati
text: Buat pecinta jamur wajib kesini, segala olahan berbagai jenis jamur ada disini dr sate, tongseng, pepes, sup, tom yum, lumpia dll. Dijamin rasanya enak n harga teejangkau. Lokasi mmg agak jauh dr pusat Kota Yogya, tepi sebanding dengan rasa makanannya

title: Jejamuran
name: Tris
text: Asal mudik ke muntilan dan mau jln2 ke jogja, pasti selalu mampir di sleman buat mkn ini. Menu yg selalu tidak lupa dipesan yaitu sate jamur dan tongseng jamur. Pas kmrn tgl 3 juni mampir pengunjungnya penuh. Tapi walaupun rame, pesanan kita cepat datangnya, mungkin krn udah dimasak duluan ya. Tapi jadinya sayurnya tidak panas lagi pas dikeluarkan, cuma hangat2 gitu. Padahal dulu waktu belum seramai skrg, makanannya waktu dikeluarkan, masih panas semua. Kyk kmrn pesan nasgor juga udah dingin, padahal nasgor kan enaknya makannya pas masih panas2. Sate jamurnya pun kmrn udah dingin. Yg panas cuma kuah tongseng aja. Tapi tetep pasti akan kembali kalo pas mudik lagi.

title: Jejamuran
name: Argi Kartika
text: Menu yang ditawarkan adalah variasi berbagai jenis masakan jamur. Parkir mudah dan luas,  ada tempat parkir khusus di seberang jalan. Harga standar,  kisaran 20k untuk menu lengkap dengan minum. Lebih murah jika memesan menu paketan.  Rasanya enak,  sate jamurnya mirip daging. Ada toilet dan musholla. Cocok untuk keluarga yang membawa anak-anak atau untuk tempat kumpul. Luas dan nyaman. Ada tempat untuk berfoto bersama. Pelayanan standar.

title: Jejamuran
name: Yusuf A.H. (yussan)
text: enak banget, tapi tiap menunya porsinya kecil2. tapi tidak apa kalo untuk coba2, nanti bisa pesan lagi jika memang cocok.

title: Jejamuran
name: Tuki Jan
text: Parkiran sangat luas makanannya pun tidak mengecewakan cocok banget buat kalian pecinta jamur

title: Jejamuran
name: Little Acan
text: Recommended Resto. Parkiran luas, suasana nyaman, ada kolam ikan terapi jadi kelebihan tersendiri. Semua menu nya dibuat dengan bahan utama Jamur. Saya nyoba sate Jamur dan Jamur goreng tepung. Enak! Parkiran nyaman, petugas Ramah, toilet bersih. Oke!

title: Jejamuran
name: Pj. Coffee
text: Rasanya enak. Tempatnya nyaman. Harga pas di kantong. Tempat parkir luas dan aman serta gratis.

title: Jejamuran
name: Isnaini Rahmawati
text: Buat kalian pecinta kuliner jamur atau kalian yang tidak bisa makan daging, kesini ajaa disini surganya berbagai olahan jamur yang mantap. Rasanya nendang, pelayanannya cepat dan ramah, serta fasilitas yang tersedia banyak. Cocok untuk family time.

title: Jejamuran
name: Fia
text: Dari luar sepi ternyata didalem lumayan rame & luas, cocok utk wisatawan tp sbg akamsi 5 menit dr rumah boleh lah sesekali mampir. Pelayanan cepat. Rasa cukup lah

title: Jejamuran
name: Anggita Sekar Prawesti
text: Pelayanan sangat baik dan cepat. Selalu ramai pengunjung terutama ketika weekend dan hari libur. Tempatnya nyaman, cocok untuk anak-anak juga. Ada kolam ikan terapi yang bisa dicoba oleh pengunjung.

title: Jejamuran
name: ani masr
text: semua menunya sangat tasty, lupa order apa aja, semuanya enak tapi satu menu yang gak cocok dilidahku sate jamur sambel kacangnya, pemiliknya ramah semua pengunjungnya disapa

title: Jejamuran
name: iren imuetzzz
text: Makanan enak, harga bersahabat

title: Jejamuran
name: jarot budi hartanto budihartanto
text: Tempatnya nyaman....rendang amur...tongseng jamur dan makanannya enak2....😊😊

title: Jejamuran
name: rizqi sulthonn
text: Makanannya enak, tapi waktu makan disini pesanan ada yg blm dateng padahal sdh lapor 2x, sampai plg pesanan juga blm dateng. All over rasa makanan enak

title: Jejamuran
name: Wisnuaji Gagat Priambada
text:
Tempatnya makin sip aja..terakhir kali dateng belom kayak gini... skrg nyaman bgt..lebih luas ...ada taman buat photo spot.... ada kolam ikannya bagus..anak2 pasti pada suka..jualan oleh2 jamur dan lain2nya...

Makanan di foto adalah:
1. rendang (enak...masih sama dg dulu)
2. Jamur pedas (enak...recommended)
3. Tumis jamur lombok ijo (cocok banget buat temen nasi)
4. Sate jamur (recommended)

Benernya ada lagi yg enak tp gak keambil fotonya..yaitu nasgor jejamuran... enak...

Parkirannya luas juga.. petugasnya sigap nyeberangin pengunjung... salut..

title: Jejamuran
name: Siti Fathonah
text:
Parkir luas, tempat makan luas, menu yg enak menurut saya sate dan tongseng jamur.
Depo oleh2 khas jejamuran terutama kripiknya jua jozzz. Sayangnya sy tdk bisa liat kebun jamurnya krn datengnya malem dan agak tergesa. Dan pasti akan tambah nikmat klo semua hidangan tersaji dalam keadaan panas.

title: Jejamuran
name: Aditya.D Septiawan
text:
Masakan lumayan enak dari berbagai macam jamur.
Bbrp masakan agak dingin, mungkin udah dimasak beberapa waktu sebelumnya dan distok biar cepat disajikan.

title: Jejamuran
name: Yohan Agus
text: Lokasi mudah dijangkau,tempat parkir luas di seberang,tempat cukup luas,pelayanan baik dan lumayan cepat,bagi penggemar olahan jamur disini tempatnya.tempat makan cukup luas,protokol kesehatan dilakukan disini termasuk pengaturan meja dan kursi.setelah masuk kita diberi daftar menu dan ditanyakan jumlah rombongan untuk menentukan nomor meja.rasa lumayan dan porsi cukup mengenyangkan.harga relatif.

title: Jejamuran
name: Regina Kezia
text: Langganan dari jaman masih ga seluas sekarang, sampai dlu pas rame bgt sampai harus parkir jauh dan dijemput shuttle bus, sekarang masih luas tp sepi banget dibanding jaman dlu sampai waiting list. Makanan harganya diatas rata2 dan porsi yg lumayan dkit dibanding dulu. Pelayanan cepat bahkan makanan keluarnya cepet banget. Cocok utk bawa keluarga karena ada playground mini, tempat melukis, ayunan, bisa kasih makan ikan juga. Kesitu ketemu ownernya yg slalu tanya ke customer bagaimana makanannya, endingnya ngobrol sejam dan dpt banyak pelajaran baru.

title: Jejamuran
name: Wanda Dwi Rachmaditya (Wanda)
text: Masakan nya enak, semua bahan daging jamur, khususnya gulai jamur nya jos..

title: Jejamuran
name: Bhernadheta Ria Anditasari
text:
Tempatnya luas, makanannya enak dan nggak harus nunggu lama. Harga pas di kantong. Banyak vegan menunya.
Buat kalian yang suka jamur harus banget ke sini, karena banyak menu makanan dan minuman yang pake jamur.

title: Jejamuran
name: Bagus Eddy Wibowo
text: Pelayanan cepat ,masakan enak terutama fuyunghai jamurnya,tekstur telurnya sangat lembut,

title: Jejamuran
name: Dion Pradhana
text: Rasanya cukup enak dengan harganya yg tidak terlalu mahal. Kalau kesini pas hari libur pasti sangat rame dan waiting list. Parkir mobilnya juga sering penuh dan harus parkir agak jauh.

title: Jejamuran
name: PinilihLinuwih TokoBuku
text: Terakhir kali ke sini, 10 tahun yang lalu 🤣 rasa satenya masih sama enaknya.. 🤤

title: Jejamuran
name: Amanah FN
text:
Rame banget!!!
Banyak spot foto yg instagramable
Pilihan menunya bervariasi
Paling suka sama sate jamur dan jamur goreng asam manis
Tongsengnya terasa mirip mie instan rasa kari
Minumnya aku suka geronimo

title: Jejamuran

Resto luas dengan berbagai menu olahan jamur, tersedia juga menu camilan kering dari jamur. Resto buka dari jam 10 pagi, namun di pagi hari menu belum lengkap, masih banyak menu yang belum siap/tersedia untuk dipesan. Sebaiknya datang menjelang makan siang agar bisa mencicipi berbagai menu yang ditawarkan.

Kami mencapai tempat ini mengikuti arahan Google maps dan lokasiny akurat. Tempat parkir tersedia luas di seberang restoran.

Tempatnya nyaman asyikkk selagi nunggu pesanan dtg kalian bisa santai rileks sejenak dng terapi ikan. Buat anak2 jg cocok lho ada kolam ikan kalian bisa kasih makan disana.. Soal rsa makan.. Eh paling endess sate jamur.. Wuihh gag kerasa kalau tu jamur berasa mkn ayam.... Wajib kalian coba ya.
Sya pertama kalinya ngajak ibuu langsung dah habis pesanan nya.  Kata beliau inakk(👌 enak) sateeenya.  Risole jamur jugaa.  Nyammiii

title: Jejamuran
name: Riski Andika S S, S.Pd.
text:
Area parkir di tempat ini cukup luas karena berada tepat di seberang lokasi utama. Tempatnya tertata dengan rapi dan bersih, memberikan kesan nyaman bagi pengunjung. Namun, teks penanda di area semak-semak sedikit tertutup oleh tanaman, sehingga perlu perhatian lebih agar terlihat jelas.

Salah satu daya tarik utama tempat ini adalah variasi menu berbahan dasar jamur yang sangat beragam dan lezat. Rasanya sebanding dengan harganya, sehingga memberikan nilai yang memuaskan bagi para pengunjung.

Selain menikmati hidangan, pengunjung juga bisa menikmati terapi ikan secara gratis, sebuah pengalaman unik yang menambah kesan relaksasi. Tidak hanya itu, tersedia juga spot foto yang menarik dengan latar kolam ikan koi, cocok untuk mengabadikan momen kunjungan.

title: Jejamuran
name: SEMBRANI TOUR

title: Jejamuran
name: Widodo Suryaputra
text:
Pertama kali makan ke sini (Sabtu/6 Mei) bersama seorang teman, "turis" lokal yang berdomisili di Brazil. Kesan pertama sangat menggoda dan langsung jatuh hati. Sangaaat nyaman dan lahap menikmati menunya, terutama sate, rendang, dan saus tiramnya.

Rasa masakannya benar-benar seperti sate ayam, rendang daging, dan ikan dimasak saus tiram, padahal semuanya dari jamur. Kokinya pinter nih! Apalagi sambil minum saparilla dingin...weeenaaak...!

Seru juga ada terapi ikannya yang bikin geli-geli gimanaa gitu. Ukuran ikan lebih besar dari ikan-ikan yang biasanya untuk terapi.Dijamin GELI buat Anda yang tak tahan geli.

HIGHLY RECOMENDED untuk resto jamur! Pengen ke sana lagiii :-D

title: Jejamuran
name: G. Angel
text:
Unique Flavor Profiles:
Lets try theirs's menu showcases a variety of mushrooms prepared in innovative ways, blending traditional Indonesian flavors with modern twists.

Signature Dishes: mmmm... love theirs mushroom satay, crispy mushroom tempura, and creamy mushroom soup — each bursting with rich, umami goodness.

Fresh Ingredients: full of shines through, making every bite flavorful and satisfying.

Cozy Ambiance: A warm, inviting atmosphere complements the food perfectly, making it ideal for casual dining or a special outing.

title: Jejamuran
name: Livia Stella
text:
Vegan friendly resto in Yogyakarta, as most of the menu are made from mushrooms a.k.a. “Jamur.” Worth a visit, because they taste and menu are varied.

Must try: Karedok Jamur, Sate Jamur, Pepes Jamur

title: Jejamuran
name: Raymond Ng
text: Enjoyed my lunch of mushroom dishes. They also have fried chicken, prawn and fishes dishes which are not on the menu.

title: Jejamuran
name: yuichiro kannagawa
text: ジョグジャカルタで地元料理を経験するならこのお店がお勧めします。エントランスを入ってすぐに様々なキノコのデコレーションがあるようにキノコ料理専門店で家族で楽しんでいる様子がうかがえます。店内はとても大きく団体用の別室も用意されております。子供用遊び場も用意されているの小さいお子さん連れの現地の皆さんにも愛されているようです。昔は無かったようですが現在は魚料理や牛肉の料理もあります。基本はハラル料理なのでアルコール類はありません。様々なキノコをインドネシアの独特な味付けで美味しくいただきました。

title: Jejamuran
name: X T
text:
Unique restaurant where almost everything on the menu is made from mushrooms.

Not everything might suit everyone’s taste (I couldn’t handle the traditional drink beras kencur) but still a good try

title: Jejamuran
name: Fadhil Amadan
text:
Jejamuran is a well-known restaurant that offers a unique dining experience with a focus on mushrooms as the star of every dish. Located just outside the hustle and bustle of Yogyakarta, Jejamuran is set in a spacious, open-air area that makes it comfortable for both small groups and large gatherings. The restaurant’s concept of mushroom-based dishes is intriguing, and the ambiance has a natural, rustic charm that fits well with their farm-to-table approach.

The food here is genuinely special, offering a wide range of dishes, from mushroom satay to crispy mushroom tempura. The variety showcases just how versatile mushrooms can be. Each dish is flavorful, and it’s fascinating to see how well mushrooms are transformed to mimic traditional meat dishes, making it a great option for vegetarians or those looking to try something different. The service is friendly, and the restaurant’s open layout makes the experience feel casual yet welcoming. If you’re curious to try an extensive menu based around mushrooms, Jejamuran is definitely worth visiting.

title: Jejamuran
name: Anova Fatimah
text: Jejamuran, a unique restaurant near Yogyakarta, puts mushrooms at the heart of every dish in a rustic, open-air setting. From mushroom satay to crispy tempura, the menu showcases the incredible versatility of mushrooms, offering flavorful options for both vegetarians and adventurous eaters. The friendly service and relaxed atmosphere make it perfect for any group. For an unforgettable mushroom-based dining experience, Jejamuran is a must-visit!

title: Jejamuran
name: Yoseph “Simeon” Dwi
text: Many choices of food menus made from various mushrooms. Also available are other typical Indonesian non-mushroom dishes such as stir-fried water spinach, etc. Both open and indoor interiors are available with adequate spaces.

title: Jejamuran
name: Alexander Limke
text: A good choice for vegetarians, as the restaurant primarily offers a variety of mushroom dishes. Upon entering, you'll receive an order form with your table number. You’ll need to fill in the form and give it to the service staff to place your order. After eating, you’ll need to take a copy to the cashier for payment. The food arrived quickly and was good. The atmosphere is warm and inviting, and you even have the opportunity to try a complimentary fish pedicure. Overall, the experience was enjoyable.

title: Jejamuran
name: Bagus Prasetya Wirawan
text: One of my favorite restaurant in Jogja. This place has always been a must-visit restaurant every now and then I visited Jogja. Serving all kinds of mushroom based foods with reasonable price and undoubtedly scrumptious taste. Sadly during my last visit, the food waiting time was way longer than my previous visit, and there were too many ants on my table which really annoyed me. Hopefully this troublesome won't happen again in my next visit, thank you.

title: Jejamuran
name: Keluarga Bontanghe
text: A very decent place to eat with your family. Because they provide spacious place, clean and comfortable seating, modern style facilities. The staffs are well organized, eaxh consumer will be directed to a dedicated empty yable. It is a good instagrammable place also. The food are plentiful, the taste is relatively good and similar to other common foods

title: Jejamuran
name: Uqik Mas
text: This restaurant is huge, my first time ever to eat in a mushroom restaurant and i liked it. Food is tasty and affordable prices, they also sell chili sauce, cake, etc in their store. The last thing is the parking lot, all i remember is they got 2 wide parking lot and its free.

title: Jejamuran
name: Kelana “Kkkecil” Keluarga Kecil
text: Great taste, the satay was really great, taste almost like meat. The place were nice also, many ponds there, various spot for taking selfies. The most important things is it tooks them no more than 20 minutes to prepare the the dishes. Amazing

title: Jejamuran
name: Shahril Affandi Radzali
text:
Its a good place for huge family. This restaurant provides huge space for huge crowd. Their service system also very systematic and the food as delivered fast to our table. They also provide enough facilities for visitors such as kids play area, prayer rooms and washrooms. They also has a store selling mushroom-based products.

But.. we did not enjoy loud live music in the middle of the noon. It just annoying as we cant have a decent conversation even with the waiters. Therefore, the owner need to make sure the sound of the live performance do not too loud in the future. Other than that, all is perfect.

title: Jejamuran
name: Andrea Pratama
text:
I like the taste of the all mushrooms here, satay, baked, and fried
Location is easy to find, spacious parking lot
The price was not cheap, but also not too high, as its basically 'Mushrooms'

title: Jejamuran
name: Melinda Ang
text: A unique place for mushroom lovers. Quite a diverse menu offering different kinds of mushroom dishes in many styles... Skewered, curries, soups, eggs and even drinks! Fear not meat lovers, there are a few chicken dishes if you don't like mushrooms THAT much. A retail store selling over-floured, deepfried mushroom crisps among other things, to finish off your visit awaits at the entrance /exit.

title: Jejamuran
name: Denny Arianto
text:
All kind Indonesian cuisine with mushroom.  The taste is great! I love it and also the "Beras Kencur" will make you fly to heaven 😁.

The only improvement needed is the atmosphere and the capacity during peak season.

Nice fish pool for the kids also available.

title: Jejamuran
name: Nolianto Ananda
text:
Everything made from mushroom (straw mushroom, oysters, ear mushroom, etc) , lot of kinds of menus. Soup, satay, tongseng, mushroom with green chilli, jamur penyet etc. Nice and cozy place, delicious food, affordable price.
You need extra effort to find this place, better use GPS.

title: Jejamuran
name: Asad Ullah
text: A fantasitic taste-heaven with unique mashroom food variety. Enjoyed my foodie experience with family.

title: Jejamuran
name: Hadi Hendra
text: Very unique mushroom-based restaurant not so far from Jogja city. Various delicious mushroom menus are available in the resto with affordable price, nice ambiance, and friendly staff. Good job!

title: Jejamuran
name: Agus Wiwanto
text:
A unique restaurant that sell variety of mushrooms as a base for their dishes.
I like its satay and tongseng, the fuyong egg is good but the crispy fried mushroom is only average.

title: Jejamuran
name: Sari Widyanti
text: Great restaurant to have lunch with family, friendly for vegetarian! Friendly and quick service, tastes good, reasonable prices, free fish spa for feet and hands, big musholla, can buy mushroom food and plant gifts, and also provide a tourist cart to the mushroom plantation.

title: Jejamuran
name: Ery Tri
text: Overall the food is good. Atmosphere is great for family gathering and comfortable. But the foods here a little bit pricey, example for pepes jamur, it cost about IDR 20k only for 1 little piece of pepes mushroom. And a tom yum jamur, wasn't taste like the real tom yum. It's more like "blimbing wuluh" soup.

title: Jejamuran
name: Indra
text: good taste good price and good service

title: Jejamuran
name: Sumiyati Abdul Chamid (Bu Sum / Bu Seno)
text:
I've just heard from my neighbour that is a sister of the Jejamuran's owner. She said that it is very crowded with visitors, especially when it is in a holiday. People said that  it's very cheap to eat dinner there with family. The menu is varied with  kinds of mushrooms. I like it very much, so I would like to go there next month insyaAllah with family.
Reading others' review, I feel more sure that I won't be disappointed to go there.

title: Jejamuran
name: Muhammad Abrian
text:
One of the most visited restaurant in Yogyakarta.

They serve all the food with mushroom as the main ingridient. you can taste mushroom satay, mushroom tom yum, musroom tongseng and many other mushroom based food.

It provides more than 100 seats. in the peak season like school holiday or long weekend you might wait to get a seat, because this restaurant is in high demand.

For the food, I recommend you to taste the mushroom satay, i think it tasted very much like meat satay.
And other thing that i like about this place is they serve it so fast, you dont have to wait too long (it was so crowded when i came here)

and dont worry about the parking space, they provide 2 large parking spaces. one of them located about 300 m from the resto but they provide shuttle bus to the resto.

price range : $1 - $4 each menu.

title: Jejamuran
name: Putri A. Smit
text: This is my second time here, previously there was a lot of variety of food, but for the second time a lot of food was not available. Me and my friends ordered mushroom satay (tasty, taste like a chicken satay with peanut sauce), fried mushroom penyet (like eating chicken penyet), mushroom rendang (not like the taste of rendang because it's sweet), fuyunghai stuffed with mushrooms (sweet), mushroom cah broccoli (fresh and tasty), tongseng mushroom (savory, tasty and a little spicy). The place is clean, there are indoor and outdoor rooms available. You can order for events. There is a prayer room and toilet, ample parking. Disability access is quite easy to get to the dining table. Overall is good!

title: Jejamuran
name: Martina Ariany
text: Loves the satay jamur, if you dont really like mushroom, the do have chicken and fish menu

title: Jejamuran
name: Rosemary Mankin
text:
A nice change from daily menu. It has a lot of variety of mushroom dishes, a heaven for vegetarian, from satay mushroom to fried Tempe.  But they also serves chicken dishes too. I recommend their tumis kangkung (sauté kangkung with mushroom) and mushroom satay.
Their dining area so large, I reckon they can fit almost 250 seats. No air conditioner though. Their parking lot large enough located across the restaurant and the chauffeur get complimentary drink.
The taste? Just like chicken satay. Uniquely, mushroom satay texture feels just like chicken satay (chicken barbecue in skewer).
When you had a chance to go to Sleman area, central Java not far from Yogyakarta city,  just go for it.

title: Jejamuran
name: Herry Wu
text:
First time i came here,coz of my Friend keep telling me to try this all menu about mushroom,,and i love it...taste was so great and the price is so affordable as well.
I love the mushroom satay,,wanna come back for the second one...next time..👍🏻

title: Jejamuran
name: Gatot Tri
text: Good vibes and ambience with nice meals. Tbh, it's little bit to much for mushroom dishes seasoning. Overall, it's a nice experience

title: Jejamuran
name: Peter Randall
text: The food dishes at this place are very cheap, yet so delicious. I am not normally one to seek out eating mushrooms, but I gave them a go and thoroughly enjoyed them. The atmosphere is the restaurant is relaxing with the open air feel. You can also purchase mushroom snacks at the gift shop if desired.

title: Jejamuran
name: Irfan Sylvanto
text: Almost all food here is made from mushroom, therefore it's suit for vegan / plant based diet. I recommend to try sate jamur and shitake fried. The cost is around 50k-60k per person depend on food & drink that you order.

title: Jejamuran
name: Reananda Hidayat Permono
text:
Such a unique meal and comfortable restaurant it is. Located in Sleman, we came here for late lunch on our way from Semarang. Jejamuran only sells jamur (mushroom) menu, such as fried rice, rendang, satay, and scrambled egg. Plenty spaces for parking car, a bus with local tourists was even there though.
Price is around 15-25k/menu. Very recommended.

title: Jejamuran
name: Gisela Shienny
text:
very crowded. u should book an appointment beforehand otherwise you would get an hour waiting list.
food's ok. satay mushroom is great :)
spacy restaurant, many variants of mushroom and there's souvenir shop.

title: Jejamuran
name: Budy Tanajaya
text: Very good g concept resto, fungi only food. Some of the dishes are too spicy for my taste. But generally it good food, with good place to hang out. Tend to be crowded in holiday season

title: Jejamuran
name: DIAN KUSMAWATI
text: Most of foods made from mushroom..with taste of Indonesian Traditional foods such as Sate Muahroom.. Rendang Mushroom.. They also sell their own brand for you to take home or as a gift...Having alot of space for parking ..

title: Jejamuran
name: Tifany Fany
text:
Good for vegan people. All menue is mushroom. They also sell cactii and mushroom plants. They have kombucha too!

But you need to wait for 15-20 minutes after you order. The place is quite popular, so many people come to eat.

title: Jejamuran
name: Gloria Y
text:
They treated the mushrooms as if it was real proteins. I'm amazed by how much effort they put into each dish.
The employees are helpful. The place is good for kids.
When you go there, the first thing you do is go to the front desk to book your table & get a menu.
It's worth the trip.

title: Jejamuran
name: Monica Andriani
text: Good price and place. So crowded and lively during my visit here. All of the food here is based on mushroom. My friend choose a family packet menu, but half of it was spicy so i end up eat just a little. But still it's an enjoyable dinner

title: Jejamuran
name: Felicia Ho
text: Served many types of mushroom dishes. They have a great concept, great food, it's just a bit far from the city. They also sell mushroom chips and other souvenirs, they also have a photo spot. Tips; the earlier you get here, the better, as most of the popular item is sold out quickly.

title: Jejamuran
name: Aditama Santosa
text: Mostly food here is mushroom, everything is about mushroom, if you cannot eat it, there are some side dish, but not much, such as chicken, noodles, etc....

title: Jejamuran
name: M Chee
text: Good food, lots of mushroom. Nice atmosphere, definitely a place to have a satisfying meal. Service was unimpressive though, staff seemed bored.

title: Jejamuran
name: Timothée “Xyala” Pineau
text: Pretty awesome place. A full menu just with mushrooms. If you don't like mushrooms, they will make you like it. Much recommended!

title: Jejamuran
name: galoeh adhiesetyo
text:
The taste of jamur satay slight different if compare 5 years ago. I like the taste before.
Overall the service was good

title: Jejamuran
name: Muhammad Umar Alfaruqi
text: It is really unique restaurant that most of the menu are mushrooms based meal. The place is spacious. Sometime there is also live music. However, for me it is a little bit too sweet. Even the fried penyet mushrooms is not spicy at all. The satay could have more peanut sauce so it can match the real satay. But after all it will return to personal preference of the customer..

title: Jejamuran
name: keisya snf
text: The place is large and comfortable. The price is relatively cheap. You can get various type of mushroom with variative cook. This restaurant also implement health protocol. The service in here all is good.

title: Jejamuran
name: rohib alfaisal
text:
great place....great food...made from mushroom...
really love it...
have a wide variety of menus...
all of em are mushroom cuisine...
there is also a mushroom theme  gift shop...
absolite delight for mushroom lover

title: Jejamuran
name: Ajeng Sitoresmi
text: Good taste. Various array of Mushroom cuisine. And they are come in quite affordable price! Only the 🍚 rice I find expensive.

title: Jejamuran
name: bumbu masakan
text: Nice taste, very big place, suitable for groupa of people, they got a lot of bus park slot

title: Jejamuran
name: Andi Purnomo
text: Great place for vegan. Taste is as original as the prime. Mostly the food are made from mushrooms. I did enjoy satay and tongseng. There are also some traditional beverages widely known as jamu. It tastes good and pretty much different than any bottled drinks out there. Dont forget to drop by in the souvenir shop.. overall, the taste is super in contrast with the price.

title: Jejamuran
name: Daniel Wahyudi
text: Fun, always full or half full. Food taste 4 star for any of them. My favorite food is rendang Namur. "Kick"

title: Jejamuran
name: Prasanda Martha Sheila
text: All about yummy mushroom food! They have large parking area. But it is such a formal place to eat like a fancy restaurant, not suitable to hang out.

title: Jejamuran
name: Bali HQ
text: This Resto only serves mushrooms. So many varieties sold here and quite tasty. Big parking area and full as very popular with the locals

title: Jejamuran
name: Tjun Sulestio
text: A unique culinary experience. I got to try assorted meat-free dishes with mushrooms as the main ingredient... and even a mocktail with enoki syrup! There is not much by way of ambience, but everything tasted great. A must try when in Yogyakarta. Highly recommended.

text:
Their mushroom satay is their main dish which i think is just okay
What I think is their highlight dish is their roasted chicken
From the size of the chicken, you can clearly see it's a farm grown chicken NOT the kind of chicken where it's raised inside a factory being injected of hormone
They marinated the chicken before roasting it making every bit tasted extremely good

Highly recommend to get the roast chicken when you're wating here

Last time,  We came at 9 am, they  had not prepared yet.

Oh the foods are mostly Indonesian & Asian food with a twist of replacingthe proteins with variety kinds of mushrooms. The service, even though it's not the fastest, but it's also good. Overall, highly recommended especially if you're into mushrooms!

place is not to close to the main road, so traffic is not so issue to get there. They have procedures from the time guests are coming until they're left, and its really² helpful.. nice thing to have this kind of service in this kind of resto.

consider coming back again.

The parking space is spacious.
Overall it's a nice restaurant to go with ypur love ones.

text:
For whoever finding new ways of serving mushrooms, you will be amazed how they can make the mushrooms tastes like the original.

The resto area is very big, even you need to park vehicles about 100m from the location but the shuttle bus provided is very quick.

The food is good, the service is amazing even you come in busiest day. The price is amazingly cheap. I think that’s because the mushrooms itself is also cheap.

I recommends this place to be visits, especially for big families and group dining.

Absolutely there's always a reason for me to comeback.

Minus are, they didn't put the menu descr. and pricre is not clear (eg. They didn't inform the price on the order list) and their waitress seems not sufficient people, which hassle since we need to search them if we've questions.

a unique place that serves good food. The price is really affordable. I think this place is very recommended. And as you can see on my picture, there is a spot where they display different kinds of mushrooms.

The service are amazing, and there are always tables available, even during peak season. Oh yeah, the food is impressive all-mushroom feast (some chicken dishes are also available). However, when it is packed, you know that it’s pre cooked and warmed up.

title: Jejamuran

You can also take a picture in this restaurant, get fish theraphy, and so many activities beside enjoy your meals.

After 3 years since my last visit.
The place is getting bigger with more tables hence increasing seating capacity.

The missing fifth star belongs to the missing sambal.

Otherwise 4 stars for a well maintained quality including cleanliness.

Cleanliness is the Indonesian standard (meaning between slightly dirty and almost disgusting), but if you been around for a while, you are already used to that. Prices very cheap. They do not serve beer, but the ice tea is better than usual in these types of restaurants.

title: Jejamuran

Any kind of mushrooms you pick work wonderfully with those cooking styles.

There are a lot of numbers of toilet (sit type and squad tye) and they are clean also. The Mushola is also kind of spacious and clean

Semi outdoor dining
Vegan and non vegan, mostly vegan
Reasonable price
Big parking areas (and they provide shuttle!!)
Clean toilets
Free fish therapy :)

However:
Long queue
And serving time is rather long, prepare about an hour from they take your order.

If you are looking healthy food in a good or hommy taste, this place is right place.
Order : Gulai, satay, tomyum with original taste, but all of them are mushroom or JAMUR.
Don't forget to buy mushroom chips for snacky time.

too bad the prayer room is very small

text: Resto Jejamuran cukup terkenal, tapi lokasinya agak jauh dari pusat kota Jogja, jadi butuh effort buat ke sini. Harganya lumayan—mungkin terasa mahal bagi warga lokal, tapi masih terjangkau untuk wisatawan luar kota. Rasa makanannya oke, tapi sayang waktu ke sana beberapa menu gak lengkap, termasuk jamur tiram yang justru favorit. Jadi agak curiga, jangan-jangan jamurnya bukan dari kebun sendiri. Tempatnya luas dan konsepnya terbuka, jadi cukup panas karena gak ada AC, tapi untungnya ada kipas angin. Fasilitas seperti mushola dan toilet tersedia dan bersih. Overall tetap menarik buat yang penasaran sama olahan jamur.

title: Jejamuran
name: Tubagus Kris Aditya
text: Ini kali kedua kita kesini bersama keluarga, terakhir kesini taun 2016, lmyn udh lama jg, sampe udh banyak perubahan dr tempat makannya semakin banyak tempat duduknya, terlebih musholanya jauh lebih luas dan nyaman. Makanan: sesuai dgn nama tempatnya it's all about Jamur 😁. Dari semua masakan jamur yg sy pesan, cm lumpia yg ga suka, dr aromanya kurang enak. Atmosphere: Suasananya lumayan ramai krn pas jam makan siang. Yg berbeda dr kunjugan sebelum2nya, varian jamur krispi yg biasa ada utk oleh2 jauh berkurang. Ohya lupa, skrg ada kolam terapi ikannya, lumayan bikin relax kaki 😁

title: Jejamuran
name: Lien Lien
text:
Hahai kamu para pemburu kuliner di Jogja...pasti udah familiar banget sama Jejamuran nih, terutama buat jamur lovers.

Di Jejamuran ini kamu bisa menikmati aneka olahan jamur, dari yang berkuah sampai yang digoreng. Pilihan menu cukup beragam. Buat kamu para vegetarian, tempat ini bisa jadi salah satu destinasi kulineranmu.  Di sini ada sate jamur, pepes jamur, jamur goreng, sop jamur, rendang jamur, jamur geprek, nasi goreng jamur, telur dadar jamur dan aneka olahan jamur lainnya.

Selain jamur, di sini juga ada ayam goreng dan ayam bakar, tempe dan tahu. Ada kudapan/snack juga lho teman, ada lumpia, risoles dan martabak.

Untuk minuman juga banyak variasinya ada minuman dingin, minuman panas dan aneka juice buah.

Untuk tempat lumayan nyaman, toilet juga bersih. Ada banyak wastafel juga.

Untuk spot foto tidak terlalu banyak. Ada sedikit taman ynag bisa menambah kesejukan.

Untuk rasa, menurut saya rata-rata. Tongseng jamurnya lumayan, tapi untuk ayam bakar dan jamur gepreknya biasa, kurang nampol pedesnya. Overall, menurut saya rasanya rata-rata.

Untuk harga dengan rasa yang rata-rata menurut saya seimbanglah.

Tapi menu jamur ini sangat baik untuk kesehatan kita supaya bisa mengurangi daging-dagingan. Jamur dimasak tongseng enak juga kok, teman.

Well, kalau kamu ke sini, pastikan kamu order tongseng jamurnya ya.

Stay safe, stay healthy, stay happy. Berkah Dalem 🙏🏻

rasanya sudah lain dari awal” dulu kesini….
kmrn lewat mampir ternyata banyak menu yg tdk ready.. harga nya sudah terlalu kejauhann juga … kenapa yaa harganya jamur bisa lebih mahall sma resto daging kambing di area selatan jogja yg ckup terkenal itu…

title: Jejamuran
name: Umi Nada
text:
Makanan:
Kami pesan tongseng jamur, rendang jamur, sate jamur, tomyam jamur, puyunghai jamur, dan tumis jamur.. semua makanan yang kami pesan rasanya ada yang enak dan ada yg B aja. Porsi msng2 makanan yang kami pesan hanya cukup untuk 1 orang sesuai dengan harganya yg terjangkau.. saran aja untuk yang mau makan disini.. jika lebih dari 1 orang ingin makan makanan yang sama, sebaiknya pesan 2 porsi khususnya untuk menu yang berkuah2 dan rendang jamur.. untuk puyung hai dan sate masih bs sharing..
Ada hal yang sedikit mengecewakan.. beberapa makanan disajikan dalam kondisi dingin.. mungkin sudah di masak sebelumnya dalam jumlah besar dan ketika ada pesanan tinggal diambil sesuai jumlah porsiannya.. Hal ini yang tidak kami harapkan dalam sebuah restoran.. ketika datang, memesan makanan, makanan baru dimasak dan kami harapkan semua makanan datang dalam keadaan panas/hangat.. lain halnya ketika kami makan di resto sistem touch screen atau prasmanan (even prasmanan pun dalam kondisi hangat karena ada penghangatnya).. oleh karena itu bintang 3 untuk makanannya

Suasana:
Ketika kami datang restoran sangat ramai, pdhl kami datang sudah jam 3 sore berarti sudah lewat jam makan siang.. untuk pengaturannya sudah tertata dengan baik.. pelayanannya mulai dari tempat parkir sampai mendapatkan meja sudah oke tidak ada keluhan

Nasi gorengnya juga bukan nasi yang kering pera (?) gitu. Ini nasinya lengket, gak cocok untuk jadi nasi goreng. Yah, plusnya jamur banyak jadi gak rugi rugi banget.

title: Jejamuran
name: Sapto Nugroho
text: Bertahun penasaran mengunjungi, suasana lumayan ramai parkir kalau sedang liburan agak jauh.... makanan standart, pelayanan penyajian amat sangat lama lebih dari 30 menit

title: Jejamuran
name: Yohna fortinatus
text: Tempat makan olahan jamur paling enak se dunia..ga ada lawan..
